title: NCLEX-RN 3500 Individual
description:
NCLEX-RN Review 3500 - Individual Version is a product of Lippincott Williams & Wilkins, a leading publisher of information for nursing students and professionals.

NCLEX-RN Review 3500 - Individual Version includes:
* More than 3,500 NCLEX-style review questions
* Pretests to evaluate strengths and weaknesses
* Customizable reviews with instant feedback
* Customizable tests with detailed analysis and feedback
* Study aids lists based on test scores

To operate NCLEX-RN Review 3500 - Individual Version, we recommend that you have the following computer equipment, at a minimum:
* Windows(r) 98
* Pentium III 450
* 128 MB RAM or more
* 80 MB of free hard-disk space
* SVGA monitor
* CD-ROM drive
* Mouse.
